  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Ontario High Court has approved the Tamil Nadu Genocide Awareness Weekly Bill",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ontario High Court has upheld the 104th Tamil Genocide Awareness Week Bill submitted to the Ontario Provincial Parliament of Canada, pointing out that it is similar to the provincial education policy that focuses on World War II and other international struggles.",
        "The 104th Tamil Massacre was tabled in the Ontario Provincial Parliament of Canada last month by the Awareness Week Act of 2021.",
        "According to the bill, a week from the 12th to the 18th of this month will be declared as Tamil Genocide Awareness Week in the State of Ontario. The bill was introduced to encourage people in the province of Ontario to learn about the Tamilnadu massacre and other massacres around the world during that week.",
        "While the Sri Lankan government has already expressed dissatisfaction with the bill, three Canadian-based diaspora organizations have recently filed a lawsuit in the Ontario High Court seeking its removal.",
        "One of those organizations, the Sri Lankan-Canadian Action Coalition, said the Tamil Genocide Awareness Week Act was unconstitutional and that the 'Tamilnadu massacre' was a misconception created by diaspora Tamils \u200b\u200bsupporting the Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) without any evidence.",
        "In such a context, the Ontario High Court has ruled in favor of enacting legislation recognizing the genocide of Tamils \u200b\u200bfor the purpose of enlightenment and remembrance.",
        "Moreover, the High Court pointed out that this is in line with the provincial education policy, which focuses on World War II and other international struggles.",
        "It is noteworthy that Canadian human rights activists and expatriate Tamils \u200b\u200bcommented that the verdict was a victory for the Tamils \u200b\u200band a very welcome one."
      ],
